{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% set page = {
  title: "Privacy Policy",
  description: "SpaceSmart Guide privacy policy - how we collect, use, and protect your data.",
  canonicalUrl: site.url + "/privacy/",
  ogImage: seo.default_image
} %}

{% block content %}
<section class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
  <header style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Last updated: {{ formatDate(now) }}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="article-body">
    <h2>1. Data We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>We collect minimal data:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email addresses</strong> — Only if you subscribe to our newsletter (optional)</li>
      <li><strong>Anonymous usage data</strong> — Via Google Analytics 4 (if enabled): pages viewed, time on page, device type, country</li>
      <li><strong>Affiliate click data</strong> — Which product links you click (for earnings tracking, no personal ID)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect: names, addresses, phone numbers, payment info, browsing history outside our site.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Newsletter delivery (only with your consent)</li>
      <li>Site improvement (aggregated analytics)</li>
      <li>Affiliate commission tracking (anonymous)</li>
      <li>Legal compliance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>First-party cookies</strong> — Newsletter dismissal, theme preference</li>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics (GA4)</strong> — Only if <code>GA4_ID</code> is configured. IP anonymization enabled. Data retention: 14 months.</li>
      <li><strong>No third-party advertising cookies</strong> — No Facebook Pixel, no ad network trackers</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can disable cookies in your browser. The site works fully without them.</p>

    <h2>4. Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>When you click an affiliate link (Amazon, etc.):</p>
    <ul>
      <li>We earn a commission if you purchase (at no extra cost to you)</li>
      <li>The merchant (Amazon) receives your click ID for attribution</li>
      <li>We do <strong>not</strong> receive your personal info from the merchant</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your data. We share only:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>With Google (Analytics) — aggregated, anonymized</li>
      <li>With Amazon (affiliate) — click ID only, no personal data</li>
      <li>When legally required</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Newsletter emails: Until you unsubscribe (link in every email)</li>
      <li>GA4 data: 14 months (auto-delete)</li>
      <li>Server logs: 30 days</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <p>You can request:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access to your data</li>
      <li>Deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Opt-out of analytics</li>
      <li>Unsubscribe from newsletter (instant, via email footer)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Email <a href="mailto:privacy@spacesmartguide.com">privacy@spacesmartguide.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h2>9. Security</h2>
    <p>HTTPS everywhere. No databases storing personal data. Static site = minimal attack surface.</p>

    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>Updates posted here with new "Last updated" date. Material changes emailed to subscribers.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@spacesmartguide.com">privacy@spacesmartguide.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</section>
{% endblock %}